high_descs: Turn around and go to the small table by the wall.
Pick up the keys from the table.
Turn left and head to the window.
Go to the small black table on the other side of the room.
Pick up the keys off the black short table.
Take the keys to the lamp nearby.
Leave the keys on the switch of the lamp when you turn it on.
anns.task_desc: Take keys from the black table, leave them on the lamp when you turn it on.

high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room to the black table.

Turn to the left and walk across the room to the lamp in the corner.
